# Refresh-cooldown lock — written on every ingest (background or manual)
# to coordinate concurrent users via fcntl.flock. Only needs to coordinate
# within one Streamlit Cloud container's lifetime; cross-deploy persistence
# isn't required, so we don't ship it in git.
data/last_refresh.json

